sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Taskmaster
    participant Beads
    participant Conductor
    participant Bot1 as Bot 1
    participant Bot2 as Bot 2
    participant Bot3 as Bot 3
    
    User->>Taskmaster: Project plan
    Taskmaster->>Beads: Create task graph
    Beads-->>Taskmaster: Top-level bead ID
    Taskmaster-->>User: Tasks created
    
    User->>Conductor: Top-level bead ID
    Conductor->>Beads: Analyze dependencies
    
    Conductor->>Bot1: Assign task (no blockers)
    Conductor->>Bot2: Assign task (no blockers)
    
    Bot1->>Bot1: Work on task
    Bot1-->>Conductor: Task complete
    
    Conductor->>Beads: Check dependencies
    Conductor->>Bot3: Assign task (blockers resolved)
    
    Bot2->>Bot2: Work on task
    Bot2-->>Conductor: Task complete
    
    Bot3->>Bot3: Work on task
    Bot3-->>Conductor: Task complete
    
    Conductor->>Beads: Check all child beads
    Beads-->>Conductor: All complete
    Conductor->>Beads: Mark top-level complete
    Conductor-->>User: All work done
